00:38:10.728 --> 00:38:11.848
groups as well as

645
00:38:13.288 --> 00:38:17.188
academic and the FDA as well. Many

646
00:38:17.228 --> 00:38:20.628
of the early degraders had a QT prolongation as an early

647
00:38:20.708 --> 00:38:24.008
observation, and people began to think, well, is it part of the mechanism?

648
00:38:24.088 --> 00:38:27.728
Is it something driven by this act of trying to force proteins through the

